msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh! <2.pa>You're that Hylian I met at\n"
"<3.se_co>Zora River<4.re_co>!\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>Are you here at Prince Sidon's request?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>Well, King Dorephan and Prince Sidon\n"
"are waiting for you.<7.pa> Please help them!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ohoho... <2.pa>So you're back.<3.pa>\n"
"You're that Hylian our Prince Sidon\n"
"brought here, aren't you?\n"
"Please go and meet with him right away."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid "<1.so>Good morning."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid "<1.so>Good day."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid "<1.so>Good evening."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid "<1.so>Yes, sir! <2.pa>Nothing to report, sir!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: raw
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid "<1.so>...Yes? <2.pa>Did you need something?<3.ra>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ohoho, a Hylian, eh?<2.pa> The path\n"
"to <3.se_co>Zora's Domain<4.re_co> is paved with\n"
"monsters, is it not?\n"
"Here in the domain, <5.pa>we are currently\n"
"recruiting warriors to join Prince Sidon\n"
"in his fight.\n"
"Please hurry up and meet with him."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid "<1.so>Farewell!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>At the top of these stairs is the throne\n"
"room of King Dorephan and his son,\n"
"Prince Sidon."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk11"
msgid "<1.so>Me?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk12"
msgid "<1.so>My name is Tottika.<2.pa> I'm a novice soldier."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: single_choice
msgctxt "talk13"
msgid "<1.so>By the way...<2.pa>HYLIAN...<3.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You managed to make it to <2.se_co>Zora's Domain<3.re_co>\n"
"all by yourself, eh?\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>That would mean you've got a pretty\n"
"reliable weapon on you, yes?<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: sound
#. 6: set_colour (red)
#. 7: reset_colour
#. 8: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk15"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I see.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I've been supplied a <2.se_co>silverscale spear<3.re_co>.<4.pa>\n"
"I have no complaints about it, but...\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>There are rumors of a <6.se_co>legendary blade<7.re_co>...<8.pa>\n"
"one that chooses its wielder."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk16"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I want to become an important soldier...<2.pa>\n"
"one who's worthy of being chosen by\n"
"a legendary weapon!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk17"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hylian!<2.pa> Have you seen?!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"The rain that has been falling ever since\n"
"<3.se_co>Divine Beast Vah Ruta<4.re_co> was angered...<5.pa>\n"
"has finally stopped!\n"
"Was that you and Prince Sidon?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk18"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh! <2.pa>Hylian!<3.pa> You have done us a\n"
"great service!\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Captain Bazz filled me in.<5.pa> He told me you\n"
"are the Champion who visited Zora's\n"
"Domain 100 years ago. Or...something."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk19"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Great Hylian Champion...<2.pa> Thank you so\n"
"much for all you have done for us."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk20"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Now, even the elders who were so down\n"
"on you are likely looking upon you with\n"
"regard and triumph!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk21"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Because of your glorious deeds, I'm sure\n"
"the elders will be content to let the\n"
"subject of Mipha finally wash away."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
#. 5: pause (short)
#. 6: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Here in <2.se_co>Zora's Domain<3.re_co>, we're currently\n"
"recruiting warriors to join Prince Sidon\n"
"in his noble struggle.\n"
"<4.so>However, the elders are...stubborn.<5.pa>\n"
"They are wholly against outsiders\n"
"getting involved in Zora affairs.\n"
"But King Dorephan, as well as the young\n"
"folk, are ready to accept anyone's help...<6.pa>\n"
"Well, so long as they are trustworthy.\n"
"If you wish to learn more, please go and\n"
"speak with King Dorephan directly."
msgstr ""

